像这样的黑客在线雇用网站是<a href="http://www.cbsnews.com/news/hackers-for-hire-freelance-cyber-spies-at-your-service/" target="_blank">最新兴起的网站服务方式</a>，类似的网站还有<a href="http://neighborhoodhacker.com/" target="_blank">neighborhoodhacker.com</a>"</p>
